<div style="position:absolute;left:50%;margin-left:-297px;top:0px;width:595px;height:842px;border-style:outset;overflow:hidden">
    <div style="position:absolute;left:0px;top:0px">
        <img src="d1062bdc-ef6d-11e9-9d71-0cc47a792c0a_id_d1062bdc-ef6d-11e9-9d71-0cc47a792c0a_files/background1.jpg" width=595 height=842></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:253.00px;top:55.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">PRIVACY POLICY</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:383.20px;top:67.05px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Effective date: September 2019</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:57.00px;top:91.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">ChildsApp privacy policy</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:57.00px;top:103.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">ChildsApp provides messaging services and other Services to users around the world. Our</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:57.00px;top:115.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Privacy Policy describes the procedures we use to process information (including messages). For</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:57.00px;top:127.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">example, what information we collect and how it affects you. Our Privacy Policy also explains</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:57.00px;top:139.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">what measures are taken to protect the confidentiality of your data.</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:57.00px;top:163.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">1.</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:163.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">GENERAL PROVISIONS</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:175.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">This Privacy Policy is an appendix to the Terms of Use posted on the Site, and regulates the</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:187.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">policy and procedural aspects of the collection, use and dissemination of personal data</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:199.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">through the Application. For the purposes of this Privacy Policy, “personal data” refers to</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:211.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">information that makes it possible to identify a person, as well as all information about person’s</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:223.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">activities, for example, about the use of the Application, if such use is directly related to</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:235.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">information that allows you to identify the user. All conditions and terms defined by the Terms</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:247.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">of Use are applicable in this Privacy Policy and have the same meaning. When using the</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:259.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Application, the Client agrees to this Privacy Policy. By registering and using the account in the</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:271.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Application, the Client allows the collection, use and dissemination of his personal data in</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:283.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">accordance with this Privacy Policy and applicable law.</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:57.00px;top:307.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">2.</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:307.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">ACQUISITION OF CUSTOMER PERSONAL DATA</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:319.00px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">Your account information.</span><span class="cls_002"> To create a ChildsApp account, you must provide your mobile phone</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:331.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">number. You regularly provide us with access to phone numbers of ChildsApp users and other</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:343.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">contacts stored in the address book of your mobile phone. You confirm that you have the right</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:355.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">to provide us with these numbers. You can add additional information to your account, such as</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:367.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">name, profile photo and status message. For more comfortable use of the Application when</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:379.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">installing the Application on a mobile device, Clients may be requested, for example, to provide</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:391.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">phone number, email address, full name, date of birth, gender, location (city).</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:403.00px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">Your contacts.</span><span class="cls_002"> To help you organize communication with other people, we can create lists of</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:415.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">your favorite contacts, and you yourself can register groups or lists, join and add to them, while</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:427.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">these groups and lists will be attached to your account information. This information is</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:439.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">included in the Client’s account through which the Client uses the Application. The Client's</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:451.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">account in the Application provides the ability to identify each Client. In addition, the</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:463.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Company’s servers store information about the Client’s activities in the Application. Personal</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:475.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">information and personal data may include some information not directly provided by the</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:487.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Client, as the Company also collects information related to access to the Application.</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:499.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Additionally, the Company has the right to collect the following information: - information about</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:511.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">the Client’s mobile device (model, version of the operating system, unique identifiers of the</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:523.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">device, as well as data on the mobile network and phone number); - information about logs</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:535.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">(log files) containing information about using the Application or viewing information using the</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:547.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Application (including, but not limited to detailed information about using the Application,</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:559.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">including search queries, phone call data, including phone numbers for incoming, outgoing</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:571.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">and redirected calls, date, time, type and duration of calls, as well as information about the</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:583.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">SMS route, IP addresses, data on hardware events, including errors and actions in the system,</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:595.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">as well as settings, type and browser language, date and time of the request and referrer URL);</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:607.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">- location information (including GPS data sent by the mobile device, data from various</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:619.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">coordinate determination technologies). Each Application Client has the right to view, edit and</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:631.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">delete personal information and personal data in his account.</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:57.00px;top:655.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">3.</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:655.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">USE OF PERSONAL DATA</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:667.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Only authorized employees of the Company who support the work of the Application have</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:679.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">access to the personal data of Clients. Such employees are required to strictly maintain</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:691.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">confidentiality and prevent third-party or unauthorized access to Clients’ personal data.</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:703.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Information related to access to the Application can be used by the Contractor to diagnose the</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:715.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">operation of the Application, as well as to ensure high quality customer service. In addition,</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:727.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">personal information and personal data can be used to analyze the behavior of Clients of the</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:739.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Application, to assess the interest shown in relation to various sections of the Application. The</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:751.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Customer’s personal information and personal data may be used by the Company for</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:763.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">administrative purposes, for example, for internal investigations of violations of the Terms of</span></div>
</div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:50%;margin-left:-297px;top:852px;width:595px;height:842px;border-style:outset;overflow:hidden">
    <div style="position:absolute;left:0px;top:0px">
        <img src="d1062bdc-ef6d-11e9-9d71-0cc47a792c0a_id_d1062bdc-ef6d-11e9-9d71-0cc47a792c0a_files/background2.jpg" width=595 height=842></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:55.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Use and this Privacy Policy. All publications written by Clients and identified by them as public</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:67.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">are published in the Application in the public domain, signed by the name specified when</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:79.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">installing the Application on the Client’s mobile device, and are available for viewing by all</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:91.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Clients of the Application. The Contractor reserves the right to share personal information and</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:103.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">personal data of Clients with the founders and managers of the Company, as well as with all</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:115.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">branches, representative offices and other companies associated with the Company, but</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:127.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">ensures to require everyone who gets access to this information to comply with the terms of</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:139.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">this Privacy Policy. The public data of the Client’s account in the Application, as well as</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:151.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">information about the actions that the Client performs in the Application, can be used by the</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:163.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Company for commercial purposes, including in advertising. The Contractor may use email</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:175.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">addresses to send updates or news of the Application. Moreover, the Client may at any time</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:187.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">refuse to receive such messages.</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:57.00px;top:211.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">4.</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:211.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">INFORMATION THAT IS COLLECTED AUTOMATICALLY BY COOKIES FILES.</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:223.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">We use cookies to ensure the operation and provision of our Services, including web Services,</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:235.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">to improve the quality of service, analyze the use of the Services and configure them in</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:247.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">accordance with user preferences. For example, they are necessary for the ChildsApp Web</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:259.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">service to work, for computers and other Web Services. In addition, we can use cookies to</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:271.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">determine which answers to frequently asked questions are most popular and to show you</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:283.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">interesting articles about our Services. Also, cookies are used to store information about your</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:295.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">preferences (language, etc.) and to configure the Services in accordance with them. </span><span class="cls_003">Support</span><span class="cls_002">.</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:307.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">You can provide us with information related to the use of our Services, including copies of your</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:319.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">messages, and your contact details so that we can provide you with technical support. For</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:331.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">example, you can email us information regarding the operation of our application or other</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:343.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">issues.</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:57.00px;top:367.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">5.</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:367.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">INFORMATION ACQUIRED FROM THIRD PARTIES. INFORMATION ABOUT YOU THAT OTHER</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:379.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">PEOPLE PROVIDE.</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:391.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">We receive information provided by other people that may contain data about you. For</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:403.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">example, when your friends use our Services, they can provide us with your phone number</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:415.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">stored in the address book of their mobile phones (just as you can provide their numbers), call</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:427.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">you or send messages to you or to the groups in which you are a member.</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:439.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Third-party organizations. We cooperate with third-party organizations that help us provide,</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:451.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">improve, analyze, customize, maintain and advertise our Services. For example, we work with</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:463.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">companies that distribute our applications, provide infrastructure, cartographic and reference</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:475.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">information, delivery systems and other systems, process payments, analyze the use of our</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:487.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Services and conduct marketing events. In some situations, these companies may provide us</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:499.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">with information about you, e.g. application marketplaces may send us reports to diagnose</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:511.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">and resolve problems.</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:523.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Third party services. We allow you to use ChildsApp Services with third party services. If you</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:535.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">use our Services with third party services, we may receive information about you from these</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:547.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">third parties, e.g., if you use the “Share on ChildsApp” button in a news service to send an</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:559.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">article published in it to your contacts, members of a group or mailing list of ChildsApp, or</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:571.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">access our Services by clicking on the link in the advertisement for our Services posted by a</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:583.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">mobile operator or device provider. Remember that third party services are governed by</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:595.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">individual terms of service and privacy policies.</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:57.00px;top:619.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">6.</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:619.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">HOW WE USE YOUR INFORMATION.</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:631.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">We use all the information we have to ensure the operation, provision, improvement, analysis,</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:643.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">configuration, support and promotion of our Services.</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:655.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Our Services. We are engaged in the provision of our Services, including user support,</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:667.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">troubleshooting, improvements and customization of our Services. We study how people use</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:679.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">our Services, analyze and use the information we have to evaluate and improve our Services,</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:691.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">conduct research, develop and test new services and functions, and also troubleshoot</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:703.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">problems. In addition, we need it to respond to your inquiries. Cookies are used to ensure the</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:715.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">operation, provision, improvement, analysis and configuration of our Services.</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:57.00px;top:739.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">7.</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:739.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">INFORMATION THAT YOU AND CHILDSAPP SHARE.</span></div>
</div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:50%;margin-left:-297px;top:1704px;width:595px;height:842px;border-style:outset;overflow:hidden">
    <div style="position:absolute;left:0px;top:0px">
        <img src="d1062bdc-ef6d-11e9-9d71-0cc47a792c0a_id_d1062bdc-ef6d-11e9-9d71-0cc47a792c0a_files/background3.jpg" width=595 height=842></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:55.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">You share your data when using our Services and communicate with them, and we share your</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:67.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">data in order to provide operation, improve, analyze, configure, support and provide you our</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:79.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Services.</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:91.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Account Information. All users of our Services can see your phone number, name and profile</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:103.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">photo, online status and status message, status of “last seen online”, and read reports,</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:115.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">although you can hide certain information from other users using the settings in our Services.</span></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;left:71.00px;top:127.00px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">Your contacts and other people. Users with whom you communicate can save and transmit</span></div>
